Platform: Windows 7 x64 Intel
JDK: 8u60 64-bit (compilation, execution)

Tried the trick as in the video (uh) launching with JDK 8u60 x86, and guess, doesn't work.
Time wasted: 3h

here is the code in ModelBatch.java

```
    public void render (final RenderableProvider renderableProvider, final Environment environment, final Shader shader) {
        final int offset = renderables.size;
        renderableProvider.getRenderables(renderables, renderablesPool);
        for (int i = offset; i < renderables.size; i++) {
            Renderable renderable = renderables.get(i);
